episodes.title: Arcay GREW UP IN A CULT 💥
episodes.description:
Hey everyone, welcome back to my channel. I’m so glad you’re here. 

In today’s video, I’m going to share something very personal and deep—my journey out of a religious cult I used to be a part of. I know, it sounds crazy, but trust me, it was a long and intense ride. I’m going to talk about the things they made me believe, the control they had over my life, and how I eventually broke free. 

If you're in a similar situation or just curious about how cults work and how they manipulate people, I hope my story helps you or gives you some insight. Don't forget to like, subscribe, and share this video—let’s keep this conversation going and support each other. 

Let me know in the comments if you’ve experienced anything similar or have questions. I’m here to help. 

#CultSurvivor #BreakingFree #LifeAfterCult #MyStory #Vlog #Healing #MentalHealth #Awareness
